ZH: 我们周末去了动物园。
EN: We went to the zoo on the weekend.

ZH: 动物园里有很多种动物。
EN: There are many different animals at the zoo.

ZH: 我最喜欢的动物是长颈鹿。
EN: My favorite animal is the giraffe.

ZH: 动物园里的猴子很调皮。
EN: The monkeys at the zoo are very mischievous.

ZH: 孩子们都喜欢去动物园。
EN: Children all love going to the zoo.

ZH: 春天是去动物园的好时候。
EN: Spring is a good time to go to the zoo.

ZH: 今天的动物园很热闹。
EN: The zoo is very lively today.

ZH: 动物园里有一只企鹅在游泳。
EN: There is a penguin swimming in the zoo.

ZH: 我带了一些萝卜去喂动物园里的兔子。
EN: I brought some carrots to feed the rabbits at the zoo.

ZH: 动物园周围有很多树。
EN: There are many trees around the zoo.

ZH: 明天的天气很适合去动物园。
EN: The weather tomorrow is perfect for going to the zoo.

ZH: 动物园的大熊猫很受欢迎。
EN: The giant pandas at the zoo are very popular.

ZH: 动物园是一个很好的户外场所。
EN: The zoo is a great outdoor venue.

ZH: 这个动物园拥有很多珍稀动物。
EN: This zoo has many rare animals.

ZH: 动物园每天都会举办不同的表演。
EN: The zoo has different performances every day.

ZH: 我们可以坐小火车游览整个动物园。
EN: We can take a small train to tour the entire zoo.

ZH: 动物园里有一个区域尽是鸟类。
EN: There is an area in the zoo that is full of birds.

ZH: 动物园的工作人员很有耐心。
EN: The zoo staff are very patient.

ZH: 我听说这个动物园离市中心很近。
EN: I heard that this zoo is very close to the city center.

ZH: 去动物园是和家人一起度过愉快时光的好方法。
EN: Going to the zoo is a great way to spend quality time with family.
